<plot>It was one of Channel four's most distinctive and evolving brands. Flava was the first black music series to showcase the best in urban music from rap to hip hop, from soul to garage and from R'n'B to Drum'n'bass! Flava consisted of 6 series and included exclusive videos from the likes of Missy Elliot and Sisqo. It also included live performances from some of the hottest acts around.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?197265</url></doc>
